de.oaam.model.oaam.library

Interface AttributeDefinition

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, OaamBaseElementA
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AttributeDefinitionImpl

    public interface AttributeDefinition
extends OaamBaseElementA
    A representation of the model object 'Attribute Definition'. Defining an additional attribute for a type of object that is mandatory for each instance of that object in the model. For instance define a serial number attribute for all device types as a string attribute

    The following features are supported:

    • Data Type
    • Target
    See Also:
    LibraryPackage.getAttributeDefinition()
